                <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A15A5/324: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chairman of the American Delegation</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Davis</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-12-13T18:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 13, 1934—6 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>52. Your 70, December 12, 10 p.m. I feel that the points which you made in
                    connection with Craigie’s observations were extremely well put.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
